text: Garennes-sur-Eure is a commune in the Eure department in northern France. The 19th-century French painter Alfred-Henri Bramtot (1852–1894) died in Garennes- sur-Eure. ==Population== ==See also== *Communes of the Eure department ==References== ==External links== *Official site Category:Communes of Eure
